MP: Detective Michele Pagan

MP: I.D. #8059. Offense number 05-368. Today's date is March 18, 2005. Today's time, by my watch, is approximately 12:54. Present is [redacted]. Reference to a control call to 561-333-0180.
(Dialing number)
UNK: Hello?
SG: Is Haley there?
UNK: No, she's working. She won't be home til later.
[Redacted]: Okay. Thanks.
UNK: Okay.
[Redacted]: Bye. She won't be home until later. She's working.
(Dialing number)
UNK: Hello?
[Redacted]: Hello again. I'm sorry. Do you know what time Haley will get back?
UNK: I don't know cause I'm not sure if she's working a double or not. But she might be back between 3 and 4.
SG: Okay. Thank you.
UNK: Alright.
MP: I.D. #8059 continuing the control call to Haley. Time now by my watch is 4:21 on the 18th. Present is [redacted].
(Dialing number)
Page 1 of 4
07/26/17 Page 11 of 81 Public Records Request No.: 17-295 DOJ-OGR-00031103
